    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Menu
    Menu Class provides a GUI for managing NFL players, including adding, viewing, comparing stats, and removing players *
    NFLApp
    The NFLApp class serves as the entry point for the NFL Management System application.
    Player
    The Player class represents an NFL player, including their name, position, team, and associated stats.
    PlayerService
    The PlayerService class provides methods for managing players and their statistics within a database, including retrieving, adding, and removing players.
    Stats
    The Stats class represents various statistical metrics for an NFL player, including passing, rushing, receiving, and kicking statistics.
